# Salesforce MCP Server Selection Policy

## MCP Server

| Server | Role | When to Use |
|---|---|---|
| `user-Salesforce DX` | **Primary execution server** — 47 tools covering org operations, LWC tooling, code analysis, LDS/GraphQL, schema describe, data ops. Requires org alias + directory context. | All Salesforce interactions: SOQL, deploy, retrieve, Apex tests, code analysis, LWC dev assistance, schema operations |

**Fallback:** SF CLI (`sf ...`) when `Salesforce DX` is unavailable or fails.

---

